metadata.name: Cineworld Group plc
metadata.description: Cineworld Group plc engages in the cinema business. It is also involved in financing, retail, cinema property leasing, property, ticket booking, film distribution, advertising, general partner, and gift promotion activities. The company operates its cinema sites under the Regal, United Artists, Edwards theatres, Cineworld, Picturehouse, Cinema City, Yes Planet, and Rav-Chen brands. As of December 31, 2020, it operated 9,311 screens in 767 sites in the United States, the United Kingdom, Ireland, Poland, Israel, Hungary, Romania, the Czech Republic, Bulgaria, and Slovakia. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Brentford, the United Kingdom.
